# Client-side
<client>
<features>
NTLM
SSL
!SSPI
</features>
<server>
http
</server>
<name>
HTTP with NTLM authorization and custom workstation
</name>
<command>
http://%HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT/%TESTNUMBER -u testuser:testpass --ntlm --login-options LOCALHOSTNAME=TESTSTATION
</command>
</client>

